23
92
00:02:26,065 --> 00:02:27,433
Shin Seol Ro. (Korean royal cuisine)

24
96
00:02:27,433 --> 00:02:29,435
Shin, shin, Seol Ro?

25
100
00:02:30,192 --> 00:02:32,171
What's that, grandpa?

26
104
00:02:32,171 --> 00:02:34,273
You're too much, really.

27
108
00:02:34,273 --> 00:02:37,243
Grandpa, why do you ask for things like that at a porridge restaurant?

28
112
00:02:37,243 --> 00:02:40,646
So far you've ordered Ja Jang Myeon, Mae Gi Mae UnTang and . . .

29
116
