34
136
00:02:58,531 --> 00:03:00,666
Ah, Tang Pyong Chae . . .

35
140
00:03:00,666 --> 00:03:06,072
Don't think of talking back to an elder. Just bring the food out.

36
144
00:03:45,368 --> 00:03:49,048
Grandpa, does it taste that good?

37
148
00:03:49,048 --> 00:03:50,549
