Make sure to bring it back next time you come!

47
188
00:04:24,951 --> 00:04:26,686
The more I see you . . .

48
192
00:04:27,787 --> 00:04:29,655
the more you seem like a lotus.

49
196
00:04:30,723 --> 00:04:32,892
A lotus?

50
200
00:04:32,892 --> 00:04:35,728
Do you know why a lotus blossoms in mud?

51
204
00:04:36,729 --> 00:04:37,363
What?

52
208
