82
328
00:06:23,727 --> 00:06:26,638
AAHHHH!  Kang San!  Lightly.  OWWW!

83
332
00:06:26,638 --> 00:06:28,293
Softly, Kang San.

84
336
00:06:29,632 --> 00:06:31,177
It hurts, it hurts. Kang San, softly.

85
340
00:07:01,173 --> 00:07:02,308
Stupid!

86
344
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:07,413
