87
348
00:07:08,647 --> 00:07:11,150
You!  Just wait 'til you get here . . .

88
352
00:07:11,150 --> 00:07:12,251
You're dead.

89
356
00:07:25,097 --> 00:07:28,033
I will come back soon.

90
360
00:07:28,033 --> 00:07:29,968
