91
364
00:07:29,968 --> 00:07:32,438
I love you, Geum Jan Di.

92
368
00:07:48,754 --> 00:07:50,156
Hello?

93
372
00:07:52,091 --> 00:07:53,659
Yes.  It's me.

94
376
00:07:56,361 --> 00:07:58,296
Really?

95
380
00:07:58,296 --> 00:08:00,966
Ehh . . . really?!

96
384
00:08:03,569 --> 00:08:05,638
Mom!  Dad!

97
388
00:08:05,638 --> 00:08:07,706
What's with all the screaming this late at night?

98
392
00:08:07,706 --> 00:08:10,042
You must have finally gotten a call from Master Joon Pyo.

99
396
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:12,845
Mom, Dad, they said you got a job!

100
400
00:08:12,845 --> 00:08:14,480
- Oh god!
- What?

101
405
00:08:17,381 --> 00:08:18,250
Hello?

102
409
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:20,185
Yes, this is Geum Il Bong.

103
413
00:08:20,185 --> 00:08:21,554
Yes, yes . . . thank you.

104
417
00:08:21,554 --> 00:08:23,756
Yes! Yes! By 8:00? Okay!

105
421
00:08:23,756 --> 00:08:25,558
Okay! I understand! We'll be there!

106
425
00:08:33,165 --> 00:08:34,533
Yes, manager.

107
429
00:08:36,135 --> 00:08:37,403
Thank you.

108
433
00:08:38,070 --> 00:08:41,640
Please make sure they don't find out.

109
437
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:51,183
Embattled by appointing Kang Hee Soo as Chairman, ShinHwa Group insists
 that this crisis will turn into opportunity.

110
442
00:08:51,183 --> 00:08:54,153
