Honey

116
466
00:10:35,421 --> 00:10:37,189
Why are you just standing there?

117
470
00:10:37,656 --> 00:10:38,557
Honey..

118
474
00:10:38,557 --> 00:10:40,859
Did you see a ghost or something?

119
478
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,729
Pinch me.

120
482
00:10:48,367 --> 00:10:51,236
Ah!  People say they like live, moving sculptures.

121
486
00:10:51,937 --> 00:10:53,205
They really are.

122
490
00:12:04,938 --> 00:12:08,374
You still haven't gone to the hospital?

123
494
00:12:08,374 --> 00:12:11,778
I went.   I already went.

124
498
00:12:11,778 --> 00:12:13,379
