127
510
00:12:42,709 --> 00:12:43,676
What?

128
514
00:12:44,444 --> 00:12:46,212
What you want to say to Joon Pyo.

129
518
00:12:47,313 --> 00:12:49,148
There's a way to get this to him.

130
522
00:12:49,949 --> 00:12:53,152
It was hard to get in touch with him after the funeral...

131
526
00:12:53,152 --> 00:12:55,088
But this time it will definitely get there.

132
530
00:12:59,358 --> 00:13:01,427
This is so sudden.

133
534
00:13:01,427 --> 00:13:04,464
I don't really have anything to say to him.

134
538
00:13:04,464 --> 00:13:06,599
Okay, begin!

135
542
00:13:14,374 --> 00:13:15,975
I can't do this sort of thing.

136
546
00:13:24,717 --> 00:13:25,618
Goo Joon Pyo,

137
550
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,088
Can you hear me?

138
554
00:13:33,259 --> 00:13:36,763
Since you've been gone I've thought of you every day.

139
558
00:13:39,699 --> 00:13:43,703
But why is it the only times I can remember are when we fought?

140
562
00:13:46,839 --> 00:13:48,408
But isn't it strange . . .

141
566
00:13:51,444 --> 00:13:54,580
Even though i can only think of the times we fought...

142
570
00:13:55,448 --> 00:13:58,317
Whenever I think of you, I smile.

143
574
00:14:08,194 --> 00:14:09,395
Goo Joon Pyo,

144
578
00:14:12,764 --> 00:14:14,534
you're doing well, right?

145
582
00:14:17,303 --> 00:14:19,772
When are you going to come fight with me?

146
586
00:17:07,173 --> 00:17:08,674
You find me irresistable don't you?

147
590
00:17:12,879 --> 00:17:16,949
There's yet to be a girl that hasn't fallen for me after seeing me like this.

148
594
00:17:17,350 --> 00:17:18,884
Who's fallen for who?

149
598
00:17:20,186 --> 00:17:22,021
I came here because I have something to say.

150
602
00:17:22,021 --> 00:17:23,656
About Joon Pyo and Jan Di?

151
606
00:17:26,158 --> 00:17:27,026
Yes.

152
610
00:17:31,764 --> 00:17:32,765
Tell me...

153
614
00:17:34,734 --> 00:17:36,102
About?

154
618
00:17:36,102 --> 00:17:38,137
You still haven't changed you mind about

155
622
00:17:38,137 --> 00:17:40,940
waiting for the one person of your destiny?

156
626
00:17:42,486 --> 00:17:43,809
That doesn't have anything to do with this.

157
630
00:17:45,542 --> 00:17:50,249
Do you think Joon Pyo is really Jan Di's partner in life?

158
634
00:17:51,284 --> 00:17:55,054
Eternal partners or soulmates?  Can that be right?

159
638
00:17:56,555 --> 00:17:57,889
That . . .

160
642
00:17:57,889 --> 00:18:01,594
Miss Ga Eul, you're applying your beliefs to Geum Jan Di

161
646
00:18:03,295 --> 00:18:04,230
What do you mean?

162
650
00:18:05,731 --> 00:18:09,168
If it were me, I'd use that time to search for my own soulmate.

163
654
00:18:09,168 --> 00:18:13,272
