166
666
00:18:34,293 --> 00:18:36,195
Sunbae, you believe in it too, don't you?

167
670
00:18:38,297 --> 00:18:40,232
Soulmates.

168
674
00:18:40,232 --> 00:18:44,135
That uncertained true love that you'll spend the rest of your life with.

169
678
00:18:44,135 --> 00:18:48,207
I think that you also believe that such a true love exists.

170
682
00:18:49,934 --> 00:18:50,910
What?

171
686
00:18:51,744 --> 00:18:54,447
